(announcer)
Next time, on a very special
Clone High.

20:42.233 --> 20:44.567
Will Abe and Joan's
student films reveal

20:44.567 --> 20:46.600
their true feelings
for one another?

20:46.600 --> 20:50.733
How will Scudworth get himself
out of another dangerous pickle?

20:50.733 --> 20:53.233
And what will become of Gandhi?

20:53.233 --> 20:55.867
I'd tell you, but I haven't
seen the episode yet.

20:55.867 --> 20:57.367
They were supposed
to send it to me,

20:57.367 --> 20:59.800
but there's this guy at work
who totally hates me.

20:59.800 --> 21:04.267
If he gets me fired,
I'm gonna kill his dog.

